Description:
Welcome to the Light side, I have the right words to make your sales accelerate faster than Han Solo's Millennium Falcon!

All geek puns aside, you've come across the Gig of a professional freelance copywriter, writer & PR, eager to provide your website with compelling content for your existing & potential customers.

In today's busy digital marketplace, high-quality content marketing will:

* make you outshine your competitors;
* build trust & engagement with your clients => a good reputation;
* ultimately, improve your SEO efforts & conversions.

How I can make sure that the Force will be with you always:

* I will write creative & SEO optimised content for any required page on your website/blog;
* I will do my¬†research like a devoted ex-journalist (old habits die hard);
* I will adapt the tone-of-voice to suit the context & the audience;
* I will deliver impeccable spelling & grammar in US & UK English, Romanian, and French;
* I will offer you marketing consultancy based on my 5+ years experience in Journalism, Advertising & PR.

If you think we'd make a good team, let's have a chat about your needs & expectations in private.
